data.oai_dc:dc: De novo contigs from RNA-Seq of the whitefish liver transcriptome
Excel spreadsheet with de novo contigs from RNA-Seq of the whitefish liver transcriptome. Contig consensus sequences and gene expression values (RPKM) for dwarf and normal whitefish are presented.
